tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    website_id INT,
    page_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    activity VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE page_views (
    view_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID,
    page_id UUID,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE website_actions (
    action_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    action_name TEXT,
    action_description TEXT,
    action_time TIMESTAMPTZ,
    user_id INT REFERENCES website_users(user_id)
);

CREATE TABLE website_traffic (
    traffic_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    page_id INT REFERENCES website_pages(page_id),
    user_id INT REFERENCES website_users(user_id),
    action_id INT REFERENCES website_actions(action_id),
    traffic_time TIMESTAMPTZ
);

CREATE TABLE website_visits (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_id INT,
    visit_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    page_url TEXT,
    visit_duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
    interaction_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_id INT,
    interaction_type TEXT,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    interaction_data JSONB
);

CREATE TABLE user_accounts (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT UNIQUE,
    email TEXT UNIQUE,
    password TEXT,
    account_created_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE product_views (
    view_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    view_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    view_duration INTERVAL
);

CREATE TABLE cart_items (
    item_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    visitor_id INT,
    product_id INT,
    quantity INT,
    added_to_cart_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
